                            li Building an addition onto your home.
                            li Adding a retaining wall or terracing.
                            li Extending your driveway.
                            li Replacing your deck with one of a different design.
                            li Changing the color of your home.
                            li Adding a fence of any type.
                            li Changing the landscaping, especially hard-scapes.
                            li Installing a satellite dish.
                      tr
                        td(width='610', valign='top', style='width: 7.05in; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;')
                          p.Level1Text(style='margin-top: 6.0pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0in;')
                            span(style='font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;')
                              | The
                              | following
                              u do not
                              |  constitute a change to your property:
                              o:p
                          ol(style='font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;')
                            li Remodeling the inside of your home.
                            li Replacing a retaining wall or terracing with one of identical design.
                            li Repairing your driveway.
                            li Replacing your deck with one of an identical design.
                            li Repainting your home, using the same color.
                            li Repairing a fence.
                      tr
                        td(width='610', valign='top', style='width: 7.05in; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;')
