                              u
                                span(style='font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;')
                                  | How to Request ACC Approval?
                                  o:p
                      tr
                        td(width='610', valign='top', style='width: 7.05in; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;')
                          p.Level1Text(style='margin-left: 0in;')
                            span(style='font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;')
                              | The process for requesting ACC approval of a
                              | change is formally outlined in your covenants. Heres the short version.
                              b
                                u
                                  o:p
